import React from 'react'
import "./ToggleButton.css"



const ToggleButton = props => (
        <button className="toggle-button" onClick={props.click}>
            <div className="line"/>
            <div className="line"/>
            <div className="line"/>
        </button>
    )
export default ToggleButton
